09.07.
      * fixed "edit - delete track" hangs MusE - bug (ws)
07.07.
      * fixed routing for stereo LADSPA plugins used in mono strips (ws)
      * midi import: first resolve note on/of then transform ticks to internal
        resolution (ws)
06.06.
