      - arranger/portinfo: fix update of instrument names (ws)
      - fluid synth: enable drumsets (ws)
      - fixed crash on inserting meta/ctrl/aftertouch in list
        editor (ws)
      - fixed crash in arranger when moving mouse+Alt after
        removing a track (ws)
